If you consume a monster's memory item and register it
You can imagine what you would look like if you were attacked by that monster.
Since it is an image, it has no effect on the status.
Monster memory items are available when you defeat the target monster.
You can obtain it with a certain probability.
It is possible to obtain it even if you are not hit by an H attack.
